{"tid":16423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子伏屍深水埗唐樓梯間","createTime":"2016-12-01T12:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T12:17:52.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d4357c7e7cb73b0730dcfba616e01b307684911","tid":16423,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】一名男子倒臥在深水埗一幢唐樓的梯間，其後證實已經死亡。<br />\n　　現場是深水埗南昌街39號一幢唐樓，下午1時許，一名男子倒臥梯間，昏迷不醒，街坊發現，立即報警求助。<br />\n　　救護員接報到場，經檢驗後證實男子已氣死亡。警方正封鎖現場，調查死者身分及事件起因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E4%BC%8F%E5%B1%8D%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%94%90%E6%A8%93%E6%A2%AF%E9%96%93-070000564.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25BC%258F%25E5%25B1%258D%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%2594%2590%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%25A2%25AF%25E9%2596%2593-070000564.html&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX52N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=cc681d1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E4%BC%8F%E5%B1%8D%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%94%90%E6%A8%93%E6%A2%AF%E9%96%93-070000564.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}